     infringes any patent, then your license grants under section 2 are
     automatically terminated.

11.3 Termination of your rights disqualifies you from receiving new
     licenses covering the Received Work, but it does not terminate the
     rights of those who have received copies or rights from you subject to
     this License.

11.4 To the extent permission to make copies of a Covered Work is necessary 
     for running it, such permission is not terminable.

